    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) can be reliably evaluated using this model within the defined COU. Assessment team recommends acceptance with the understanding that model applicability is bounded to the validated operating envelope.",
